{"tid":631692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冚無牌按摩院淫竇　男警扮客「放蛇」拉3女","createTime":"2018-04-16T16:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T01:44:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c605a73e19591ca83208692a0a69851a2dd691f2","tid":631692,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"灣仔警區特別職務隊，根據線報及經深入調查後，今午2時許，展開掃黃行動，派員喬裝顧客「放蛇」，於銅鑼灣勿地臣街14號一單位，搗破賣淫場所。行動中，人員拘捕3名持雙程證內地女子（24至37歲），行動中檢獲一批證物，包括按摩油及毛巾等。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名姓李（24歲）女子，涉嫌「經營賣淫場所」、「經營無牌按摩場所」及「違反逗留條件」被捕，一名姓唐（28歲）女子涉嫌「協助經營賣淫場所」、「協助經營無牌按摩場所」及「違反逗留條件」，而另一名姓李（37歲）女子則涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。3名被捕女子現被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"18abc43c3f207cecf00a1667a4877f7296460465","tid":631692,"uid":77985,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T16:55:33.000Z","msg":"嘆完先拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0689ef9464e7f68159d351ca25d4e8c8def65ef5","tid":631692,"uid":70439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"打完飛機就拉人，又食又拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef55c6c0970ea9b0ec44b1bfd56e7e0c0d4ec1b","tid":631692,"uid":172169,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046d32cc76bc376e8430bfe10e60a0068f471de4","tid":631692,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"942778e781583621ff0c84186060c4d014b84fba","tid":631692,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"唔驚愛滋？"},{"pid":"e5d442dd32ebebd4396ec7ff969dce391648eea8","tid":631692,"uid":54923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"942778e781583621ff0c84186060c4d014b84fba","tid":631692,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"唔驚愛滋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-